QuestData.Title: Bauer Backup
QuestData.Description: We've not heard anything from the coast since the Horde attack started. I need you to check in on Lieutenant Bauer at Seabreeze Village and see that they're safe.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Lieutenant Bauer at Seabreeze Village.
QuestData.RewardText: Glad to hear Felecia is safe. We could use your help here though.
